description: We have a new Summer Tournament in place from here on out. We have taken the most popular, exciting wrestlers for the season and put them in a seeded tournament. Because we have so many tournaments ( 3 weight classes, rookie cup) summer vengeance took up too many weeks for updates so we have buttoned it down to the most exciting wrestlers so that we can keep the entire year fun. Today we have two of the strongest, most powerful girls ever to grace the US mats. Kelli Provocatuer and Brandi Mae are Body builders with exquisite physiques. This match is power against power. Each girls thrust her will onto the other wrestler. They go back in forth in true power play and fight for dominance. The winner earns her prize, makes her loser worship her muscles and giant swollen clit and gets her orgasm HER way
title: New Summer Tournament. Welcome to the Big 10
